Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.50,0:01:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第五話\N逆刃刀對斬馬刀決鬥的結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.16,0:01:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.93,0:01:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!小熏小姐、禰彥\N真是個好早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼輕鬆話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.74,0:01:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個專門打架的人\N或許什麼時侯會來找碴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不能跟那種人成為對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.08,0:02:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嗎劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.08,0:02:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也非常想要這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.95,0:02:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是斬左好像有相當的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.36,0:02:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你該不會\N真的想跟那種人打架吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.32,0:02:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心無論如何要打架的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.96,0:02:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什麼時候\N都可成為你練習的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.80,0:02:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你多管閒事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼多管閒事！醜女！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼醜女\N這是你對師父該說的話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.34,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙。。。\N好痛。。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.94,0:02:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是很討厭維新志士傳說中最強\N且被歌頌為殺人者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.65,0:02:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從心底想把他打倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那麼的憎恨維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.52,0:02:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男人到底是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心你在發什麼呆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.93,0:02:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？什麼？真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿熏早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玄齊大夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.07,0:02:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊小綾小雀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥來玩來玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.51,0:03:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要玩什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.48,0:03:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家這麼為他擔心\N劍心真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看清楚左之助。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德川三百年的支配結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.94,0:03:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新時代來臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.17,0:03:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以弱者被虐待\N只能忍氣吞聲的時代結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.91,0:03:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不分上下\N四民平等的時代一定會來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們赤報隊是時代的先驅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.39,0:03:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我們要加油\N早一點創造新的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.06,0:03:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都已經聽膩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.66,0:03:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四民平等的時代來臨時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也可以改姓別人的姓嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.73,0:03:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.74,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我要隊長的姓氏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改姓相樂\N可以嗎？隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.74,0:04:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂左之助嗎？不要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字變得好奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.15,0:04:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是赤報隊的隊長相樂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.29,0:04:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敝生是官軍參謀進藤帶刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.49,0:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從下取訪的本營
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來傳達總督府的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總督府的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你。你幹什麼？！斬左！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.25,0:04:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是象小偷一樣\N鬼鬼祟祟幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.39,0:04:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我。我只是想看\N整個打架的過程。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.76,0:04:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我警告你\N這場架再怎麼說都是我的架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你如果出手\N我一定不會原諒你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.50,0:05:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了\N我並不是不相信你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.74,0:05:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於赤報隊出身的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽了拔刀齊的名字後\N一定不會這麼就算了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.24,0:05:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總而言之是拔刀齊我就沒意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你有沒有意見\N你該知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男人\N一定會被我斬左打倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.62,0:05:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳跳步。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了\N劍哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？那個人的傳說？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.14,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對。。。今天來診所看病的病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道那打架屋的很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.48,0:05:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說他好像是\N赤報隊唯一的生存者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤報隊是紅蓮隊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是，指假軍官的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假軍官？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.95,0:05:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤報隊是。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.22,0:06:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維新時代由農民商人等\N一般庶民所組成的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.93,0:06:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔任軍官的先鋒部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.93,0:06:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是對各諸侯所屬的農民們說\N稅收可減半的謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而引起所有人的混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.87,0:06:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這個罪\N被維新政府所處罰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.61,0:06:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才會\N對維新志士的劍心找碴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以發洩他的恨意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.45,0:06:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己做錯了事還心懷恨意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還在那邊亂揮斬馬刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道危險就不做這事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要去阻止給你們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊。。點心？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.06,0:06:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好壞。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小綾劍心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.80,0:06:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍哥哥跟昨天那個\N頭髮直挺挺的哥哥出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對！頭髮直挺挺的，哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿熏！\N劍心這傢伙跟打架屋的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.81,0:06:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.01,0:07:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼將要開始了拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流浪人的緋村劍心。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這支逆刃對抗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到哪裏去了？劍心。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.73,0:07:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿熏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.83,0:07:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人看到劍心跟打架屋\N往那裏的河邊去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.84,0:07:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆刃刀。。你應該看過\N這斬馬的威力了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.54,0:07:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者還沒有呢，你不要認為\N我會跟流派一樣不殺你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.05,0:07:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會死那就要看你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.52,0:07:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道！！！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍。劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.86,0:07:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.93,0:07:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.15,0:08:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.38,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪！那傢伙的斬馬刀\N再怎樣厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果打不中的話\N就一點意義也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心壓倒性的有勝力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.69,0:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使被劍心一擊擊中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.56,0:08:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在人又站起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.57,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那人很強\N不只是怪力跟斬馬刀的厲害而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被打也很強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.54,0:08:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是強者\N這就是成為傳說的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.61,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在為止全部的敵人\N被劍心的飛天御劍流一劍擊倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一擊對這個人卻沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.39,0:08:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊，打架是真的劍對打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是劍術好就會贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會倒下去的人才會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.16,0:08:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說這些話\N等到站到最後時再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅。。嗦！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打架第二幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.70,0:09:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一架我會勝的！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.62,0:09:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬馬刀的重量及巨大\N限制了進攻的招數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.56,0:09:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上下橫掃二分一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常容易看穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個來結束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左，一擊對你沒用的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.95,0:09:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.19,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逆刃刀的連擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.86,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流的「龍巢閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好。。厲害。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想再對你用劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好接受輸了的事實吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我輸。。維新志士了。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們赤報隊是假軍官？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底是怎麼一回事？進藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.75,0:10:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們私自的散佈\N年稅要減半的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很明顯的讓人心混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.99,0:10:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使維新政府失去信用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這罪而不能原諒你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.63,0:10:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體是假軍官而決定處罰你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.04,0:10:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣！\N我們也是照政府所說的去轉達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.91,0:10:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.94,0:10:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對維新政府來說\N我們轉達的年稅減半令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妨礙到他們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.72,0:10:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓各諸侯所屬的農民認同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟他們約定年稅減半也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於財正困難的維新政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那實在沒辦法實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.39,0:11:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以使赤報隊成為假軍官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他背負所有的罪狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就什麼事也沒有了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的吧。進藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣的話又怎樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.17,0:11:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們相信拯救弱者的維新政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到現在為止\N抱著必死的決心奮鬥過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對新時代懷抱理想。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.35,0:11:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭是不用說得那麼好聽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.55,0:11:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰勝的一方就是正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸的就是不好的\N只是這樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.39,0:11:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如正義吧\N弱者輸了就是不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像你們一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.54,0:11:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的任務已經完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.08,0:12:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.82,0:12:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.36,0:12:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射擊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.14,0:12:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊。。。隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我放下。。快逃走。。。\N左之助。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊？隊長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.70,0:12:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走快走。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.48,0:13:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相。相樂。。相樂隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.58,0:13:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嫁禍給赤報隊，全員都被殺了\N維新志士也。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.36,0:13:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太髒了。。太髒了。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會原諒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤報隊。。。。！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對！這個人是生存者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.80,0:13:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.60,0:13:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話\N只好用我的手來解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.51,0:13:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧！拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.68,0:13:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.75,0:13:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎。。怎麼有這種事。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.86,0:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你再靠近一步的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.59,0:13:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就切斷他們的喉嚨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.43,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比留間伍兵衛。。\N我以為你被警察捉走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.10,0:14:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了拔刀齊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.68,0:14:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妨礙我打架的人\N我一定不會饒了他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.65,0:14:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸了我會受不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.59,0:14:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伍兵衛。。。無藥可救的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.33,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑！這個距離的話\N你一定沒辦法接的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,土龍閃。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.71,0:14:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂左之助。。。\N你是赤報隊的生存者。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該是收場的時侯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最強的維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,適可而止吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.92,0:14:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對的是你們赤報隊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！明明是惡黨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.39,0:14:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還恨劍心，你是不是找錯對象了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是一堆不明事理的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們跟世間的傢伙一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.03,0:15:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的相信維新志士是正義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的小熏小姐，禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.58,0:15:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤報隊被維新政府利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而被殘酷的殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.85,0:15:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左恨維新志士\N也是有道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.89,0:15:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是斬左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.49,0:15:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相樂隊長。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.09,0:15:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我們赤報隊背負惡這一文字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.43,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抹殺這些\N正義嘴臉的維新志士們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.13,0:15:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不會饒恕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不會輸的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.57,0:15:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了來做個了斷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.11,0:15:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心把刀換過來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤報隊解散後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我成為專門打架的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.89,0:16:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用打架來過活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在打架的時侯\N所有的事都能忘記！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.66,0:16:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣過了十年我也變堅強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個堅強現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.70,0:16:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要打倒最強的維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.27,0:16:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種程度的堅強\N我來把你打倒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.18,0:16:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流「龍槌閃」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.03,0:16:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是非常的頑強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.80,0:16:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被龍槌閃擊中不倒的人\N你是第一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.00,0:16:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是已經沒辦法站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.74,0:16:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上去叫醫生！等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.58,0:16:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒！還沒有結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會倒的，我不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用赤報隊及相樂的名字在拚命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.19,0:17:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！再來啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.96,0:17:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是你打架的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤報隊教你的是打倒維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.87,0:17:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是達成維新的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.20,0:17:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉嗦！捏造出偽的新時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.11,0:17:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還在那邊擺什麼架子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.34,0:17:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說什麼維新志士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.21,0:17:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心不是這樣的維新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不理會政府大官的邀請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要用劍自由的\N繼續保護人們的流浪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.46,0:17:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只知道劍心\N是殺人拔刀齊而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就私自來找他打架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.36,0:17:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說得這麼的自私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把劍心跟其他的人比
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.26,0:17:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊！劍心是用他的一把劍\N去保護人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這麼說你還不瞭解的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.27,0:17:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明神禰彥\N代替劍心來跟你打架吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.78,0:18:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左，維新還沒有結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.48,0:18:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實新時代明治已來臨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.75,0:18:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也只是形式上的維新而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.85,0:18:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是很多人\N還活在欺侮弱小的時代中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.29,0:18:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以小生要成為流浪人\N來保護那些弱小的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.63,0:18:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這把逆刃刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.93,0:18:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人拔刀齊。。\N為了要保護人們。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.27,0:18:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想這樣才能對在明治維新\N犧牲的人們有所補償
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我去叫玄齊大夫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不一樣的。。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對新時代所抱的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟奮鬥的相樂隊長。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.75,0:18:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以這傢伙到現在為止\N還在繼續的奮鬥著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經絕望了已經放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.46,0:18:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用打架過生活而欺騙自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起。。。相樂隊長。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.37,0:19:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全輸給這個男人。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.47,0:19:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.85,0:19:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙還能生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩，全身都是而且大量出血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.69,0:19:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住院三個月，玄齊大夫也說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不死已經是奇跡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.13,0:19:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左跟其他人不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.67,0:19:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以小生出手時也不能太重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.20,0:19:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正這樣就告一段落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們去吃牛肉火鍋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.24,0:19:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！那些人是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之前的自由民權運動的壯士們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.52,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的\N喝醉酒要找我打架沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.55,0:19:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是要等你們變強之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.66,0:19:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是在住院嗎。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是能耐打的\N這種擦傷算得了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把人的身體當成玩具。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.48,0:20:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬左。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你背後的「惡」一文字。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.52,0:20:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.05,0:20:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤報隊對我來說\N已經是過去的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.19,0:20:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以將這「惡」一文字拿掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.56,0:20:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這種怪性格\N是沒有辦法改的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.36,0:20:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你嘴巴所說的\N跟欺騙的維新志士不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.67,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會跟著你的\N用這個眼睛去弄清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.21,0:20:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一件事\N我已經不是斬左了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.71,0:20:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不要打架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.78,0:20:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在只是相樂左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.41,0:20:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟現在的你\N不是殺人拔刀齊一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.69,0:21:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣如果沒有我的允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.22,0:21:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准去做流浪人，劍心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.93,0:21:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又增加了一個奇怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.16,0:21:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能又當耳邊風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最奇怪的人是你。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.50,0:21:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又白吃白喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.54,0:21:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣我們又多了一位叫\N相樂左之助的朋友

